This is helloWorlds, a collection of most simple applications.

helloWorlds indicates the code of the simplest applications, 
and also indicates the simplest method of application distribution.

This package is a sample for application developper.
To build helloWorlds, some developper's tools may be required.

Requirement:
	gcc(at least, C/C++ compiler and linker)
	autoconf(ver 2.58 or lator)
	automake(ver 1.11 or lator)
	perl(ver 5.6 or lator)


